 《芭比娃娃》导演格蕾塔·葛韦格的下一部电影是什么？ https://www.nme.com/news/film/what-is-barbie-director-greta-gerwigs-next-movie-3474993?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=what-is-barbie-director-greta-gerwigs-下一部电影Chris EdwardsSat, 29 Jul 2023 13:29:45 +0000 Film NewsNewsBarbie https://www.nme.com/?p=3474993 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/greta-gerwig-barbie.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="格蕾塔·葛韦格" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/greta-gerwig-barbie.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/greta-gerwig-barbie-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/greta-gerwig-barbie-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/greta-gerwig-barbie-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/greta-gerwig-barbie-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/greta-gerwig-barbie-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>导演表示她对她的新项目感到“兴奋”和“害怕”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/what-is-barbie-director-greta-gerwigs-next-movie-3474993">《芭比娃娃》导演格蕾塔·葛韦格的下一部电影是什么？</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/greta-gerwig-barbie.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="格蕾塔·葛韦格" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/greta-gerwig-barbie.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/greta-gerwig-barbie-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/greta-gerwig-barbie-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/greta-gerwig-barbie-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/greta-gerwig-barbie-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/greta-gerwig-barbie-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/greta-gerwig">格蕾塔·葛韦格</a>执导的<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/barbie"><em>《芭比娃娃》</em></a>电影打破了票房纪录，成为年度最受关注的电影之一。因此，导演的粉丝们已经开始期待她的下一个项目，这是可以理解的。</p><p>改编自热门美泰玩具系列的<em>芭比娃娃</em>于上周五（7 月 21 日）在电影院上映。它与<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/christopher-nolan">克里斯托弗·诺兰</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/oppenheimer"><em>《奥本海默》</em></a>在同一天首映，两部电影都受到网上“巴本海默”热议的联合宣传。</p><p>葛韦格执导的<em>《芭比娃娃》</em>上映五天在美国票房收入超过 2 亿美元（1.56 亿英镑），打破了女性导演电影首周末票房最高纪录。这部由玛格特·罗比和瑞恩·高斯林领衔主演的讽刺喜剧全球票房也超过了 5 亿美元（3.89 亿英镑），迎来了自大流行前以来电影业最繁忙的一周。</p><p>现在，随着葛韦格背后<em>《芭比娃娃》</em>在经济和评论上的成功，许多人都会好奇这位导演下一步会做什么。</p><h3>格蕾塔·葛韦格的下一部电影是什么？ </h3><figure id="attachment_3355989" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3355989" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3355989" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Great-Gerwig-Barbie-director-on-red-carpet.jpg" alt="葛韦格 (Great Gerwig) 担任 2023 年电影《芭比娃娃》导演" width="2000" height="1275" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Great-Gerwig-Barbie-director-on-red-carpet.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Great-Gerwig-Barbie-director-on-red-carpet-400x255.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Great-Gerwig-Barbie-director-on-red-carpet-800x510.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Great-Gerwig-Barbie-director-on-red-carpet-696x444.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Great-Gerwig-Barbie-director-on-red-carpet-1392x887.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/Great-Gerwig-Barbie-director-on-red-carpet-1068x681.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3355989" class="wp-caption-text">伟大的葛韦格认为执导《芭比娃娃》可能会结束她的职业生涯。图片来源：盖蒂</figcaption></figure><p>本月早些时候，据透露葛韦格将为<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/netflix">Netflix</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/fans-react-greta-gerwig-making-chronicles-narnia-films-netflix-3464260">编剧并导演<em>《纳尼亚传奇》</em>宇宙中的两部电影</a>。</p><p>在接受<a href="https://www.newyorker.com/magazine/2023/07/10/after-barbie-mattel-is-raiding-its-entire-toy-box"><em>《纽约客》</em></a>导演采访时，证实该项目将标志着 Netflix 开始更大范围地打造该系列电影和电视节目。</p><p> <em>《纳尼亚传奇》</em>是 CS Lewis 创作的七本儿童读物系列，之前曾多次被改编为舞台和银幕，最近的改编是三部迪士尼电影： <em>《狮子》、《女巫与魔衣橱》</em> 、 <em>《凯斯宾王子》</em> 、和<em>黎明踏浪号的航行</em>。</p><p>在出现在<em><a class="body-link product-links css-tjvzc4 ebsw2pb0" href="https://go.redirectingat.com/?id=127X220&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fpodcasts.apple.com%2Fus%2Fpodcast%2Finside-total-film%2Fid1477057257%3Fi%3D1000621751538%26at%3D11lDJ%26ct%3D1540253X358633275c977325a0b7cd700d6775c4&amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cosmopolitan.com%2Fuk%2Fentertainment%2Fa44625805%2Fgreta-gerwig-narnia-remake%2F&amp;xs=1&amp;xcust=%5Butm_source%7C%5Butm_campaign%7C%5Butm_medium%7C%5Bgclid%7C%5Bmsclkid%7C%5Bfbclid%7C%5Brefdomain%7C%5Bcontent_id%7C5b2917c6-7503-4200-a359-85184ecc15a1%5Bcontent_product_id%7C997cc240-a851-4a9b-a3c5-8ce5294fadbf%5Bproduct_retailer_id%7C17ed4dfe-e34f-4064-b179-df34f4fd0ee3%5Blt%7C%5Boptxid%7C%5Boptvid%7C" target="_blank" rel="noopener" data-vars-ga-outbound-link="https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/inside-total-film/id1477057257?i=1000621751538&amp;at=11lDJ&amp;ct=1540253X358633275c977325a0b7cd700d6775c4" data-vars-ga-ux-element="Hyperlink" data-vars-ga-call-to-action="Total Film Podcast" data-vars-ga-product-id="997cc240-a851-4a9b-a3c5-8ce5294fadbf" data-href="https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/inside-total-film/id1477057257?i=1000621751538&amp;at=11lDJ&amp;ct=1540253X358633275c977325a0b7cd700d6775c4" data-product-url="https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/inside-total-film/id1477057257?i=1000621751538&amp;at=11lDJ&amp;ct=1540253X358633275c977325a0b7cd700d6775c4" data-affiliate="true" data-affiliate-url="https://go.redirectingat.com/?id=127X220&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fpodcasts.apple.com%2Fus%2Fpodcast%2Finside-total-film%2Fid1477057257%3Fi%3D1000621751538%26at%3D11lDJ%26ct%3D1540253X358633275c977325a0b7cd700d6775c4" data-affiliate-network="{}" data-vars-ga-media-role="" data-vars-ga-media-type="" data-vars-ga-product-brand="podcasts.apple.com" data-vars-ga-product-price="" data-vars-ga-product-retailer-id="17ed4dfe-e34f-4064-b179-df34f4fd0ee3" data-vars-ga-product-sem3-brand="podcasts.apple.com" data-vars-ga-product-sem3-category="" data-vars-ga-gallery-id="" data-vars-ga-link-treatment="(not set) | (not set)" data-skimlinks-tracking="[utm_source|[utm_campaign|[utm_medium|[gclid|[msclkid|[fbclid|[refdomain|[content_id|5b2917c6-7503-4200-a359-85184ecc15a1[content_product_id|997cc240-a851-4a9b-a3c5-8ce5294fadbf[product_retailer_id|17ed4dfe-e34f-4064-b179-df34f4fd0ee3[lt|[optxid|[optvid|">Total Film Podcast</a></em>上时，葛韦格表示，她对开始改编作品感到“害怕”和“兴奋”。</p><p> “我什至还没有真正开始拥抱它，但我确实害怕它，这感觉是一个很好的起点，”她说。</p><p> “我认为当我感到害怕时，这总是一个好兆头。也许当我不再害怕时，我会想，“也许我不应该这么做。”不，我很害怕它。这是非凡的。这很令人兴奋。”</p><p>由于该项目仍处于开发的早期阶段，人们对葛韦格的改编将采取什么形式知之甚少，而选角细节在一段时间内也不太可能透露。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/what-is-barbie-director-greta-gerwigs-next-movie-3474993">《芭比娃娃》导演格蕾塔·葛韦格的下一部电影是什么？</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 Drake 在 Travis Scott 的《Meltdown》合作中瞄准了 Pusha T 和 Pharrell https://www.nme.com/news/music/drake-takes-aim-at-pusha-t-and-pharrell-on-travis-scotts-meltdown-collab-3474998?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=drake-瞄准普沙·T 和法雷尔在特拉维斯·斯科特的熔断合作Will RichardsSat, 29 Jul 2023 13:29:39 +0000 Music NewsNewsRap https://www.nme.com/?p=3474998 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/drake-pharrell-pusha-getty-comp.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="德雷克" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/drake-pharrell-pusha-getty-comp.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/drake-pharrell-pusha-getty-comp-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/drake-pharrell-pusha-getty-comp-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/drake-pharrell-pusha-getty-comp-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/drake-pharrell-pusha-getty-comp-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/drake-pharrell-pusha-getty-comp-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>在同一首歌中，歌迷推测斯科特鄙视了蒂莫西·柴勒梅德</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/drake-takes-aim-at-pusha-t-and-pharrell-on-travis-scotts-meltdown-collab-3474998">Drake 在 Travis Scott 的“Meltdown”合作中针对 Pusha T 和 Pharrell 的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/drake-pharrell-pusha-getty-comp.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="德雷克" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/drake-pharrell-pusha-getty-comp.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/drake-pharrell-pusha-getty-comp-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/drake-pharrell-pusha-getty-comp-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/drake-pharrell-pusha-getty-comp-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/drake-pharrell-pusha-getty-comp-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/drake-pharrell-pusha-getty-comp-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/drake">Drake</a>重新点燃了与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pusha-t">Pusha T 的</a>不和，并在与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/travis-scott">Travis Scott</a>合作的新作品《Meltdown》中将矛头指向了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pharrell">Pharrell</a> 。</p><p>这两位说唱歌手长期以来一直在歌曲中互相攻击，但他们的争执在 2018 年达到了顶峰，当时<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/drake-diss-track-pusha-t-kanye-west-2325887">Pusha-T 在《红外线》节目中提到了 Drake 使用了一位名叫昆汀·米勒 (Quentin Miller) 的代笔人的说法</a>。然后说唱歌手们开始了一段简短的来回diss曲目。</p><p>现在，在 Scott 于昨天（7 月 28 日）发行的新专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/travis-scotts-utopia-album-credits-feature-beyonce-sza-kanye-west-daft-punks-guy-manuel-and-more-3474735">《Utopia》</a>中的一首曲目中，Drake 再次对 Push 进行了攻击，同时也将 Pharrell 也带入了画面。</p><p><em>他说唱道：“我把从老板那里买的链子融化了/他妈的那些狗屎传统/因为V不在身边，成员们就把路易斯挂了/他们甚至没有穿那狗屎。”</em></p><p>听下面的曲目。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Travis Scott - MELTDOWN（官方音频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/LuKm4L9ryB0?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>在《Meltdown》的其他地方，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/travis-scott">特拉维斯·斯科特的</a>粉丝们一直猜测<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/travis-scott-appears-to-diss-timothee-chalamet-over-kylie-jenner-on-utopia-track-meltdown-3474853">这位说唱歌手在这首歌中对演员蒂莫西·柴勒梅德进行了侮辱</a>。</p><p>在歌曲第二节的结尾，《火焰》提到了查拉梅在即将上映的电影<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/wonka"><em>《旺卡》</em></a>中扮演的角色威利·旺卡。</p><p> <em>“包裹奶酪，包裹我，因为我有财产（包裹，奶酪，包裹）/巧克力AP和巧克力Vs（Vs），拥有威利旺卡工厂（Vs）/像卡路里一样燃烧运动员，找到另一个像我一样热的火焰，婊子，”</em>他说唱。</p><p>粉丝们认为，这位说唱歌手之所以对这位演员不屑一顾，是因为柴勒梅德是真人秀明星凯莉·詹纳的绯闻男友。詹纳是斯科特的前夫，两人育有两个孩子，一个是 5 岁的女儿，名叫斯托米，另一个是 13 个月大的女儿，名叫艾尔。</p><p>斯科特的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/travis-scotts-utopia-album-credits-feature-beyonce-sza-kanye-west-daft-punks-guy-manuel-and-more-3474735">《乌托邦》专辑由</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/beyonce">碧昂丝</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sza">SZA</a> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kanye-west">坎耶·维斯特</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/daft-punk">傻朋克</a>乐队的盖伊·曼努埃尔等人出演。除了上映之外，一部名为<em>《马克西穆斯马戏团》</em>的新电影正在电影院上映。</p><p>在其他地方， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/drake-has-bought-tupacs-ring-at-auction-for-1million-3474928">Drake 在拍卖会上以 100 万美元（78 万英镑）的价格买下了属于 Tupac Shakur 的标志性戒指</a>。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/drake-takes-aim-at-pusha-t-and-pharrell-on-travis-scotts-meltdown-collab-3474998">Drake 在 Travis Scott 的“Meltdown”合作中针对 Pusha T 和 Pharrell 的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
